56
00:02:57,030 --> 00:02:58,290
Looks like

57
00:02:58,829 --> 00:03:00,750
I underestimated you.

58
00:03:01,420 --> 00:03:02,440
Your Majesty,

59
00:03:02,820 --> 00:03:04,960
you are no longer what you were.

60
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:07,350
I should thank you for that.

61
00:03:08,100 --> 00:03:09,600
I'll take my leave!

62
