88
00:04:53,510 --> 00:04:55,240
That's why His Majesty is ill!

89
00:04:55,590 --> 00:04:56,550
Your Highness!

90
00:04:59,260 --> 00:05:03,860
♫Dancing alone in the clouds with colorful sleeves♫

91
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,600
