105
00:05:45,030 --> 00:05:46,430
So,

106
00:05:46,450 --> 00:05:48,210
it remains to be seen

107
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,770
who will be the prisoner.

108
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,320
Who do you think you are?

109
00:05:53,030 --> 00:05:54,920
How dare you harbor such delusions?

110
00:05:56,159 --> 00:05:57,340
Guards!

111
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,760
Take her away.

112
00:05:59,790 --> 00:06:00,040
Yes!

113
00:06:00,070 --> 00:06:00,630
Yes!

114
00:06:03,050 --> 00:06:04,130
Let go of me!

115
00:06:04,150 --> 00:06:04,710
You...

116
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:06,180
How dare you lay hands on me!

117
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:06,640
Your Highness!

118
00:06:06,670 --> 00:06:07,330
Your Majesty!

119
00:06:07,350 --> 00:06:08,190
Your Majesty!

120
00:06:08,590 --> 00:06:09,910
Let go of me!

121
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:18,830
