125
00:06:25,260 --> 00:06:26,740
She's planning a rebellion!

126
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:27,710
Li Luo!

127
00:06:31,210 --> 00:06:32,090
Your Highness.

128
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,540
Go tell my father

129
00:06:33,570 --> 00:06:35,570
His Majesty is gravely ill,

130
00:06:35,590 --> 00:06:36,909
and Nangong Ying has treacherous intentions.

131
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:38,120
His Majesty is in danger.

132
00:06:38,150 --> 00:06:40,000
Tell him to come and save His Majesty.

133
00:06:40,540 --> 00:06:41,750
Go now!

134
00:06:41,970 --> 00:06:42,810
Yes.

135
00:07:02,300 --> 00:07:03,880
What took you so long?

136
00:07:04,500 --> 00:07:05,470
Are you...

137
00:07:06,190 --> 00:07:07,630
trying to play a trick again?

138
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:16,210
I know what you want to do.

139
00:07:16,370 --> 00:07:17,490
I can help you.

140
00:07:18,670 --> 00:07:19,970
Help me with what?

141
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:26,060
Just now, you put on an act in front of the princess

142
00:07:26,270 --> 00:07:29,010
because you want her to tell King of Nanjiang you're ill,

143
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,660
so that they can rise in rebellion in advance.

144
00:07:30,690 --> 00:07:32,090
I just...

145
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:34,590
added fuel to the fire.

146
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:37,780
Ying, if you were a man,

147
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:39,760
you would certainly become an official.

148
00:07:40,970 --> 00:07:42,770
I don't fight for power or wealth.

149
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,710
It's not because I'm a woman.

150
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:48,840
It's because I'm not interested in them.

151
00:07:53,159 --> 00:07:54,720
Everything under heaven

152
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:56,159
belongs to the emperor.

153
00:07:56,180 --> 00:07:57,600
All within the boundaries

154
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:59,260
are the emperor's subordinates.

155
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,620
I, the king of Nanjiang,

156
00:08:00,650 --> 00:08:02,310
once swore an oath

157
00:08:02,740 --> 00:08:05,750
to serve the wise emperor of Great Zhou until my dying breath.

158
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:07,510
But the current emperor

159
00:08:07,590 --> 00:08:09,550
cares only for romance and indulgence,

160
00:08:09,700 --> 00:08:11,620
disregarding ethics!

161
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,900
Today,

162
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,840
if you are willing to side with me,

163
00:08:14,870 --> 00:08:16,230
once we succeed,

164
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:18,990
you will all be founding heroes of the new regime!

165
00:08:19,020 --> 00:08:21,280
-I swear to follow you till my dying breath!
-I swear to follow you till my dying breath!

166
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:32,659
