167
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:33,500
-Kill!
-Kill!

168
00:08:33,530 --> 00:08:34,380
-Kill!
-Kill!

169
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,270
-Kill!
-Kill!

170
00:08:35,289 --> 00:08:36,280
-Kill!
-Kill!

171
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,330
Su Wuyang,

172
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,150
your days are numbered.

173
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:43,510
And you have no heir.

174
00:08:43,539 --> 00:08:44,700
Let me

175
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:46,550
replace you to sit on the throne.

176
00:08:47,460 --> 00:08:49,680
Su Wuyang, issue an edict now

177
00:08:49,970 --> 00:08:51,550
to abdicate the throne to me.

178
00:08:51,570 --> 00:08:54,360
