180
00:08:59,650 --> 00:09:01,480
Are you sure you want me to abdicate?

181
00:09:07,260 --> 00:09:08,660
I want to sit

182
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:11,340
on the throne for a few more days.

183
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:14,320
So King of Nanjiang, no need for you to worry.

184
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:15,920
Guards!

185
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:17,710
Seize Su Wuyang!

186
00:09:27,990 --> 00:09:29,950
To root out all your accomplices,

187
00:09:29,970 --> 00:09:32,230
