188
00:09:38,740 --> 00:09:39,990
Pass my imperial decree:

189
00:09:40,820 --> 00:09:42,550
King of Nanjiang has committed treason,

190
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:43,760
attempting to rebel!

191
00:09:43,780 --> 00:09:44,870
His crime is unforgivable!

192
00:09:45,170 --> 00:09:46,370
Send him to the imperial prison now!

193
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:47,560
